
"smart_sources:_007.Books/Real Marriage/Real Marriage 📕.md": {"path":"_007.Books/Real Marriage/Real Marriage 📕.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"wbq6ss","at":1772113914964},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1673443742000,"size":2690,"at":1772113914964,"hash":"wbq6ss"},"blocks":{"#Real Marriage":[1,64],"#Real Marriage#{1}":[3,4],"#Real Marriage#Metadata":[5,64],"#Real Marriage#Metadata#{1}":[6,6],"#Real Marriage#Metadata#{2}":[7,7],"#Real Marriage#Metadata#{3}":[8,9],"#Real Marriage#Metadata#{4}":[10,64]},"outlinks":[{"title":"rw-book-cover","target":"https://readwise-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/media/uploaded_book_covers/profile_40775/e26dd71b-6690-4528-9b16-7fd32c3c40b4.jpg","line":3,"embedded":true},{"title":"Mark Driscoll","target":"Mark Driscoll","line":6},{"title":"Marriage; Relationships","target":"Marriage; Relationships","line":8},{"title":"Martin Luther King and His wife Katie","target":"Martin Luther King and His wife Katie","line":10},{"title":"Marriage is about friendship.","target":"Marriage is about friendship.","line":12},{"title":"Fruitfulness of Wife and Husban serving God together.","target":"Fruitfulness of Wife and Husban serving God together.","line":14},{"title":"Action before feeling - Action promotes feelings","target":"Action before feeling - Action promotes feelings","line":16},{"title":"Create habits of doing things together","target":"Create habits of doing things together","line":18},{"title":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","target":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","line":20},{"title":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","target":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","line":22},{"title":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","target":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","line":24},{"title":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","target":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","line":26},{"title":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","target":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","line":28},{"title":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","target":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","line":30},{"title":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","target":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","line":32},{"title":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","target":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","line":34},{"title":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","target":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","line":36},{"title":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","target":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","line":38},{"title":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","target":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","line":40},{"title":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","target":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","line":42},{"title":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","target":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","line":44},{"title":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","target":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","line":46},{"title":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","target":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","line":48},{"title":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","target":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","line":50},{"title":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","target":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","line":52},{"title":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","target":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","line":54},{"title":"Sex","target":"Sex","line":56},{"title":"Planning in family","target":"Planning in family","line":58},{"title":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","target":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","line":60},{"title":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","target":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","line":62},{"title":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","target":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","line":64}],"metadata":{"tags":["#books"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
