nt need to be \"figured out\".","target":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","line":20},{"title":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","target":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","line":22},{"title":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","target":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","line":24},{"title":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","target":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","line":26},{"title":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","target":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","line":28},{"title":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","target":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","line":30},{"title":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","target":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","line":32},{"title":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","target":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","line":34},{"title":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","target":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","line":36},{"title":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","target":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","line":38},{"title":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","target":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","line":40},{"title":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","target":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","line":42},{"title":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","target":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","line":44},{"title":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","target":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","line":46},{"title":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","target":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","line":48},{"title":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","target":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","line":50},{"title":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","target":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","line":52},{"title":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","target":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","line":54},{"title":"Sex","target":"Sex","line":56},{"title":"Planning in family","target":"Planning in family","line":58},{"title":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","target":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","line":60},{"title":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","target":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","line":62},{"title":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","target":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","line":64}],"metadata":{"tags":["#books"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"wbq6ss","at":1772114197088}},"smart_blocks:_007.Books/Real Marriage/Real Marriage 📕.md#Real Marriage": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04911351,0.05524302,-0.05308866,-0.02647246,0.00216252,0.02826274,-0.02178038,0.02082267,0.03452513,-0.00016309,0.04923671,0.0012322,0.05684226,0.02738435,0.05164348,0.00977419,-0.00552356,0.02724253,-0.12557343,0.05767872,0.06651033,-0.01490014,0.00817416,-0.06021024,0.05766203,0.06395425,-0.05707821,-0.0273154,-0.03891936,-0.15985164,-0.00628437,0.06633508,-0.00362679,0.06008622,0.010563,-0.0341176,-0.03823474,0.03850862,-0.01631388,0.0470955,0.0414313,0.01914166,0.03390957,-0.03566203,-0.00408183,0.04552087,-0.02283818,0.02134448,0.00681251,-0.03291588,-0.02882669,0.02218793,-0.02677048,0.01389136,-0.01074283,0.01837658,0.01645765,0.0465287,0.05032137,0.05454791,0.06807484,0.03592452,-0.1848197,0.07765545,-0.01626851,-0.00861716,0.01087868,0.00031503,0.05143612,0.04663229,-0.01461751,0.05156351,-0.03201959,0.0482724,0.01021758,-0.04006736,0.01153646,-0.08681472,-0.04917721,-0.02707349,-0.00726034,0.02185673,-0.01797925,0.01592695,-0.09044875,-0.01392511,-0.00562082,-0.05982145,0.0386