e":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","target":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","line":38},{"title":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","target":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","line":40},{"title":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","target":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","line":42},{"title":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","target":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","line":44},{"title":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","target":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","line":46},{"title":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","target":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","line":48},{"title":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","target":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","line":50},{"title":"Sex","target":"Sex","line":52},{"title":"Planning in family","target":"Planning in family","line":54},{"title":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","target":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","line":56},{"title":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","target":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","line":58},{"title":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","target":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","line":60}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"15q69oi","at":1772114197598}},
