158149,0.06188913,0.01458038,0.16554293,-0.02880339,0.06774635,-0.02409536,0.07296081,0.02296915,0.06073773,-0.02034719,-0.03377295,0.0373041,-0.01199674,-0.0009507,0.04564802,-0.03343223,0.01152114,-0.00975466,0.00720314,-0.02551996,0.00013656,0.0288126,0.05331244,-0.00331971,0.11375055,-0.02332144,-0.00776625,-0.06471578,0.03643771,-0.03847036,-0.03436223,0.02497535,0.00726099,0.03655957,-0.02866098,0.02222001,-0.03454745,0.03305556,-0.04226746,0.00689333,-0.00306906,0.02201902,0.03855379,0.10178851,-0.00710456],"last_embed":{"hash":"87szk","tokens":460}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"87szk","at":1772114197848},"key":"_007.Books/Real Marriage/Real Marriage 📕.md#Real Marriage#Metadata#{4}","lines":[10,64],"size":2386,"outlinks":[{"title":"Martin Luther King and His wife Katie","target":"Martin Luther King and His wife Katie","line":1},{"title":"Marriage is about friendship.","target":"Marriage is about friendship.","line":3},{"title":"Fruitfulness of Wife and Husban serving God together.","target":"Fruitfulness of Wife and Husban serving God together.","line":5},{"title":"Action before feeling - Action promotes feelings","target":"Action before feeling - Action promotes feelings","line":7},{"title":"Create habits of doing things together","target":"Create habits of doing things together","line":9},{"title":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","target":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","line":11},{"title":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","target":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","line":13},{"title":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","target":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","line":15},{"title":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","target":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","line":17},{"title":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","target":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","line":19},{"title":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","target":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","line":21},{"title":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","target":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","line":23},{"title":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","target":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","line":25},{"title":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","target":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","line":27},{"title":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","target":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","line":29},{"title":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","target":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","line":31},{"title":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","target":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","line":33},{"title":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","target":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","line":35},{"title":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","target":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","line":37},{"title":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","target":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","line":39},{"title":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","target":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","line":41},{"title":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","target":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","line":43},{"title":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","target":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","line":45},{"title":"Sex","target":"Sex","line":47},{"title":"Planning in family","target":"Planning in family","line":49},{"title":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","target":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","line":51},{"title":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","target":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","line":53},{"title":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","target":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","line":55}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"87szk","at":1772114197848}},
